{"word":"Girdle","slug":"girdle","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Girdle</b> Worn by:<br/> - The high priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=4'>Exo 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=39'>Exo 28:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=29'>Exo 39:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=7'>Lev 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=4'>Lev 16:4</a> <br/> - Other priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=40'>Exo 28:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=9'>Exo 29:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=13'>Lev 8:13</a> <br/> - Women<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=24'>Isa 3:24</a> <br/> Embroidered<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=8'>Exo 28:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=28'>Exo 28:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=5'>Exo 29:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=7'>Lev 8:7</a><br/> Made of linen<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=24'>Pro 31:24</a><br/> Made of leather<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=8'>2Ki 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=4'>Mat 3:4</a><br/> Traffic in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=31&verse=24'>Pro 31:24</a><br/> Used to bear arms<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=4'>1Sa 18:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=8'>2Sa 20:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=21'>2Ki 3:21</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a h